replies.body:
I've had my fair share of struggles in life (they include depression, anxiety, and being a trans woman) so League has always been an escape for me.
When everything seemed like it was crumbling around me League gave me something to focus on and it helped to block everything else out. That feeling of progression and improvement from day-to-day has been a huge motivation for me to get up every morning.
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
